room_title: Escape room "Party Hard" by Quest Room in Los Angeles
room_address: 170 South Western Avenue, Los Angeles, CA 90004
room_description:
The first thing you notice is that your head hurts and the light is blinding. Looking around, you see the remnants of the party the night before. You remember some of what happened, but most of it is a blur. Worst of all, the groom (or bride) is gone and the door is locked!
Can you piece together last night's events, find your missing friend, and save the wedding? Or will you find out, first-hand, the risks of Partying too Hard?
